mind-flash (1.0.5) unstable; urgency=low

  * add tooltip for filter icon
  * add window drag-to-move support on topbar
  * add update check via `api.github.com`
  * add Markdown link style support (as default, backward compatible)
  * update Ctrl+V with enhanced response with Mime content
  * dirty hack: reset keystroke list when Enter key released
  * move current configurable items to config file ('/opt/mind-flash/res/config.ini')
  * add user config file support ('~/.mf/config.ini')

 -- iamhyc <sudofree@163.com>  Tue, 17 Nov 2020 23:59:59 +0000

